{"title":"参观登封有感","authors":["陈荒煤"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"参观登封有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈荒煤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉万千耸如林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁大军遍山坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把伏牛一扫平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄竞将帅旗夺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战鼓声声催日落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉火万丈照颍河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓烟如云锁嵩山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁流奔腾震中岳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到登封县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿觉眼界高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬头望嵩山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云缠住腰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产文化双跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄心还比嵩山高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说一穷二白不能横扫？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要白沙入库，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颍河归槽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嵩山伏牛齐献宝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不分男女老少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个诗兴豪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看小高炉、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诵诗台到处高耸入云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄知多少！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管叫钢铁粮食卫星成群抛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过中岳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破云霄。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}